name: E-Commerce UI KIT
description:
I designed this candle shop around a year ago, made it in less than 1 week just for fun and as a challenge with my design skills.


Now I want to share it with the community hoping could be helpful to someone. The kit contains:


  • Desktop & Mobile Wireframes Lo-Fi
  • Desktop & Mobile Wireframes Hi-Fi
  • Components
  • Prototype
  • Usability Benchmarks
  • Mockups
  • Brand & Socials
